title: cgo failure on arm (symbol lookup error, undefined symbol)
body:
misc/cgo/test fails:

/tmp/go-build074453444/_home/pi/go/misc/cgo/test/_test/test.test: symbol lookup error:
SansTypeface /tmp/go-build074453444/_home/pi/go/misc/cgo/test/_test/test.test: undefined
symbol: SansTypeface
exit status 127
(repeated)

pi@raspberrypi ~ $ go version
go version devel +e96ca5d8ecc3 Wed May 01 14:31:42 2013 -0700 linux/arm
pi@raspberrypi ~ $ uname -a
Linux raspberrypi 3.6.11+ #427 PREEMPT Fri Apr 26 20:53:06 BST 2013 armv6l GNU/Linux
